===================
DummyKit 0.1 README
===================

This framework is used to attract developers. It helps demonstrating dummy
development methodology.

Maintainers: John Doe <john@doe.eu>
Authors: You, John Doe, Nobody

To know more about DummyKit:
<http://www.etoile-project.com/etoile/mediawiki/index.php?title=DummyKit>


Build and Install
-----------------

Read INSTALL document.


Mac OS X support
----------------

DummyKit is not yet supported on Mac OS X.
An Xcode project could be created to build it.


Developer Notes
===============

Example
-------

1) Create a dummy:

	dummy = [[PartOfDummy alloc] init];

2) Destroy dummies:

	RELEASE([dummies collect]);


Tests suite
-----------

UnitKit (bundled with Etoile) is required.

    Steps to produce a test bundle and run tests suite:

    * make test=yes 

    * ukrun DummyKit.bundle
